    <item>
      <title>塞勒表示他愿意就加密货币问题为特朗普提供建议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/saylor-says-he-d-be-willing-to-advise-trump-on-crypto-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 联合创始人兼董事长 Michael Saylor 表示，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普需要，他愿意就加密货币或数字货币向他提供建议。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/saylor-says-he-d-be-willing-to-advise-trump-on-crypto-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 16:38:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
