    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 的 Saylor 想要更多“智能杠杆”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/microstrategy-s-saylor-wants-to-add-more-intelligent-leverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 联合创始人兼董事长迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 表示，一旦当前的筹款计划用尽，这家互联网时代的软件制造商将转向杠杆比特币代理计划，将更多精力放在固定收益证券上，以筹集资金购买加密货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/microstrategy-s-saylor-wants-to-add-more-intelligent-leverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
